{"tid":1326463,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[最後共識] 721 去邊","createTime":"2019-07-17T08:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T14:27:29.000Z","uid":272630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e8bebd3fa2007087b6806f1a6fb4f5606e41bd34","tid":1326463,"uid":272630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"跟大隊，然後 be water<br />\n民陣今日下晝已經見記者公佈遊行安排<br />\n<br />\nfor fact check:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/714859385639081/?notif_id=1563350343674072&not;if_t=live_video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F714859385639081%2F%3Fnotif_id%3D1563350343674072%C2%ACif_t%3Dlive_video&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5aua9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=cbb8894c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/714859385639081/?notif_id=1563350343674072&not;if_t=live_video</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67271076_2360458540668190_5289873092611407872_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQmhPMHTRz3t-3Tdk908UjXIyvM_bDTyLygtibnqWRYA8XoK9RnW-KPrYDCDxWuU6DY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=9fad866592008ec6cf592a00bf1a9cbd&amp;oe=5DBB7870\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67271076_2360458540668190_5289873092611407872_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQmhPMHTRz3t-3Tdk908UjXIyvM_bDTyLygtibnqWRYA8XoK9RnW-KPrYDCDxWuU6DY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3D9fad866592008ec6cf592a00bf1a9cbd%26oe%3D5DBB7870&h=e3bb91bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【 721重要通知 】<br />\n<br />\n經過兩日商討，民陣有信心721遊行會取得不反對通知書。以下為最新的行動安排︰<br />\n<br />\n獨立調查 捍衛法治 守護真相 重申五大訴求<br />\n2019年7月21日（日）<br />\n下午3時維園集合起步，往終審法院，在遮打道結束遊行<br />\n<br />\n====Q&amp;A====<br />\n1. 為何將集會改遊行？<br />\n民陣得悉原定各區地區遊行日期都有所更改，並考慮到近日局勢，認為改為遊行較為適當。<br />\n<br />\n2. 為何將終點定在中環？<br />\n今次遊行，重中之重的訴求是要求成立由法官主持的獨立調查委員會，我們認為遊行到終審法院正義女神像前，突顯我們的訴求，正是為了捍衛香港的法治。<br />\n<br />\n3. 民陣721後會有其他行動嗎？<br />\n目前可以預視到的行動包括在8月31日（人大831決定五周年）、10月1日等，民間有意發起與五大訴求相關行動。<br />\n<br />\n至於其他時間，則視乎局勢發展，尤其是林鄭月娥政府的回應。"},{"pid":"7e277f984cb958303a3bc6a7dbf14be821d89736","tid":1326463,"uid":272630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:36:57.000Z","msg":"由今日起淨係推 721 嘅 post！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1325940\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1325940</a>"},{"pid":"fbb817cfe30c5832976aaea5f97bb286211361b1","tid":1326463,"uid":228458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講。<br />\n唔好意思，阻一阻你。<br />\n[急救人入]野餐急救檢討<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1323710\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1323710</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"573a1655872603d472df7a4c0bc4aa62ef7059a4","tid":1326463,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:44:41.000Z","msg":"終點之後走邊好？"},{"pid":"1118b6214895fdd3dbca720d588789a0ae3b5f0d","tid":1326463,"uid":272630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"573a1655872603d472df7a4c0bc4aa62ef7059a4","tid":1326463,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:44:41.000Z","msg":"終點之後走邊好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T08:47:55.000Z","msg":"be water 臨場應變"},{"pid":"a3accfa30e95811ba86aab6256c79665380714f7","tid":1326463,"uid":49083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"推"}]}